<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scents & Co. | Perfume Shop</title>
    <style>
        /* --- General Styling --- */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #fcf8f5;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #4a3b32;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e0d5cc;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* --- Shop Section --- */
        .perfume-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .perfume-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .perfume-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .perfume-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b5835a;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e6dfd9;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        button {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #b5835a;
        }

        /* --- Alternatives Section --- */
        .alternatives-box {
            background: #f0e6df;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .filter-select {
            padding: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* --- Cart Section --- */
        .cart-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .total {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .checkout-btn {
            background: #27ae60;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .checkout-btn:hover {
            background: #219653;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>✨ SCENTS & CO. ✨</h1>
        <p>Find your signature scent or its perfect alternative</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <section class="alternatives-box">
            <h2>🔍 Find Perfume Alternatives</h2>
            <p>Select a fragrance family to view matching alternatives:</p>
            <br>
            <select id="scentFilter" class="filter-select" onchange="filterPerfumes()">
                <option value="all">Show All Fragrances</option>
                <option value="Fresh & Citrus">Fresh & Citrus</option>
                <option value="Warm & Spicy">Warm & Spicy</option>
                <option value="Floral & Sweet">Floral & Sweet</option>
            </select>
        </section>

        <h2>🛒 Our Collection</h2>
        <div class="perfume-grid" id="perfumeGrid">
            <div class="perfume-card" data-category="Warm & Spicy">
                <div>
                    <div class="perfume-img">🪵</div>
                    <h3>Midnight Noir</h3>
                    <span class="tag">Warm & Spicy</span>
                    <p>Notes of oud wood, amber, and rich vanilla.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="price">$85.00</div>
                    <button onclick="addToCart('Midnight Noir', 85)">Add to Order</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="perfume-card" data-category="Warm & Spicy">
                <div>
                    <div class="perfume-img">🍂</div>
                    <h3>Spice Horizon (Alternative)</h3>
                    <span class="tag">Warm & Spicy</span>
                    <p>A lighter alternative to Midnight Noir featuring cinnamon and tobacco leaves.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="price">$45.00</div>
                    <button onclick="addToCart('Spice Horizon (Alternative)', 45)">Add to Order</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="perfume-card" data-category="Fresh & Citrus">
                <div>
                    <div class="perfume-img">🍋</div>
                    <h3>Citrus Breeze</h3>
                    <span class="tag">Fresh & Citrus</span>
                    <p>Energetic burst of Italian bergamot and crisp sea salt.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="price">$75.00</div>
                    <button onclick="addToCart('Citrus Breeze', 75)">Add to Order</button>
